+ Understand How\nAuto Loader Works
++ Auto Loader
+++_ Structured Streaming source
+++_ Monitors cloud storage for new files
+++_ Each file processed exactly once
++ Detection Modes
+++_ Directory listing: periodic scan
+++_ File notification: event-driven
+++_ Notification preferred for large scale
-- File Notification Mode
---_ Cloud notification services (e.g. Azure)
---_ Lower latency, fewer API calls
---_ Enable file events on Unity Catalog external location
-- State Management
---_ Checkpoint tracks processed files
---_ Resume after interruption
---_ No manual state management needed
@endmindmap
